                <h2>About OOTD</h2>
                <p> OOTD was created by three awesome St. Louis Kode with Klossy girls.</p>
                <p>"This idea started out as a simple t-shirt generator, however it spiraled into this amazing outfit generator for daily inspiration in fashion. I'm so happy and proud of this project. I handled more of the homepage (the frontend). One of my favorite seasons is fall, because of the fashion! I love wearing boots, jackets, and nice cozy sweaters."
                - Mia Hines</p>
                <p> "I love this website not just because it was designed by my partners and I, but because we learned so much in the process. I've had many days where I was like "Ugh, I don't know what to wear today!" This gets rid of those problems because then I can choose what I want to wear and see it on the computer. I handled most of the directions that the computer was going to use (the back end; ruby). My favorite season is fall/spring, I love wearing comfy shirts paired with basketball or running shorts." -Scarlett Patton</p>
                <p> "One of my favorite parts about this website was the whole creation process. I worked on finding the pictures and helping to design OOTD. I love fashion because it inspires me. I really enjoy wearing clothes that connect with me personally. My favorite pieces are jeans, tennis shoes, boots, t-shirts, and dresses."<br>-Erica Greenberg</p>
